<bibl><author>Goette</author>, <title level="m">MDAIRA</title> 92 (<date value="1985" notBefore="1985" notAfter="1985" exact="both">1985</date>), 318, no. <biblScope>IV.3</biblScope></bibl>. Text published by
<bibl type="hbi" n="ALA"><author>Roueché</author>, <title level="m">Aphrodisias in Late Antiquity</title>
no. <biblScope>145</biblScope> and Plate xxxiii</bibl> whence <bibl n="PHI"><author>McCabe</author> <title level="m">PHI Aphrodisias</title> <biblScope n="257538">655</biblScope></bibl>. Text and statue discussed most recently by <bibl><author>Smith</author> (2002)</bibl></p>
      </div>

